{"about_the_game":"Swords and Hexes is a charming and witty adventure-RPG set in a world of Polygonia, where an ultimate artifact of power, the 'One True Hex', has broken into six shards and spread across the known realms. To be able to save the world from the evil that wishes to restore the hex to its former state, our hero must defeat strong unrelenting foes, forge friendships with the unlikeliest of characters and survive the absurd and humorous challenges that are set before him. <br><br>Swords and Hexes includes a unique multiplayer mode, that pins players against each other in a board-game-like duel, to determine who was the brains and the brawn for a decisive strategic victory. Players collect natural resources and use them to create mighty armies and subjugate their opponents.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448730/extras/Steam_Library_Hero.02.png?t=1731063793\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448730/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731063793","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448730/page.bg.jpg?t=1731063793","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448730/12eaf2896d86c898e699a6ebe04fd29cf59e0195/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731063793","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2448730/12eaf2896d86c898e699a6ebe04fd29cf59e0195/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731063793","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"LAN PvP","id":47},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"In-App Purchases","id":35},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>COMMUNITY</h